WEBVTT

00:01:57.966 --> 00:02:02.339
which the Nazis had converted
into a concentration camp.

00:02:03.522 --> 00:02:05.386
I was there for 10 months.

00:02:05.752 --> 00:02:07.774
I laid railroad tracks,

00:02:07.798 --> 00:02:10.490
I exterminated vermin,

00:02:10.514 --> 00:02:12.077
I made baskets,

00:02:12.101 --> 00:02:13.307
and after 10 months,

00:02:13.331 --> 00:02:18.823
about 2,000 of us
were loaded into cattle cars,

00:02:18.847 --> 00:02:22.410
the doors were closed,
and we were shipped east.

00:02:23.649 --> 00:02:26.206
For three days, we traveled like that,

00:02:26.230 --> 00:02:28.117
and when we were unloaded,

00:02:28.141 --> 00:02:31.887
we were smelling of urine and of feces,